  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Marketing/Storage/Processing: Amazon Sustainable Management Project (PAGES)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project objective is to enable the poor and vulnerable populations of the Amazon to restore parts of the rainforest in Maranh&#xE3;o with sustainable use systems. The project would support family farmers and traditional communities in reversing the decline in productivity caused by the downward cycle of degradation of the agroecosystem and enable the State to adopt policies and legislation and build capacities to enhance conservation and restoration of the Amazon forest in Maranh&#xE3;o.</narrative>
  </description>
